<title>Ilay havoana natao hoe: Kalvary FFPM96</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ilay havoana
 Natao hoe Kalvary,
 No tany namonoana,
 Ny Tompo Jesosy;
 O ! tsarovy re !
 Maty ory tao
 Jeso Tompo lehibe
 Hanavotra anao.

[V2]
 Jereo ny Tomponao,
 Tazanonao irý,
 Ka andrandrao ny masonao,
 Fa io no Kalvary !
 O ! tsarovy re ! ..sns.

[V3]
 Hevero Kalvary,
 Fa tao ny Tomponao ;
 Tsarovinao ny nentiny
 Mba hamonjena anao!
 O ! tsarovy re ! ..sns.

[V4]
 Tsinjovy Kalvary,
 Fa Jeso Tomponao,
 Nijaly tany raha tetý,
 Ka maty Izy tao !
 O ! tsarovy re ! ..sns.</lyrics>
</song>